description: Try our easy to follow Chicken & vegetable soup recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Chicken & vegetable soup Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: macro chicken breast fillets free range

recipeInstructions.text: Add penne pasta, cauliflower and pumpkin to soup and cook for 10 minutes or until softened. Add chicken and cook for 2 minutes to heat through. Ladle soup into serving bowls and scatter with parmesan, parsley and toasted pepitas. Serve with crisp tortillas.
